query:
SELECT 
  e.id,
  e.name,
  e.email,
  e.managerId,
  m.name as managerName,
  e.departmentId,
  e.gerencia,
  e.diretoria,
  e.secao,
  e.active
FROM employees e
LEFT JOIN employees m ON e.managerId = m.id
WHERE e.name LIKE '%Geane%' 
   OR e.name LIKE '%Rodrigo%' 
   OR e.name LIKE '%Mazuca%' 
   OR e.name LIKE '%Conselho%'
   OR e.gerencia LIKE '%Geo%'
   OR e.diretoria LIKE '%Geo%'
   OR e.secao LIKE '%Geo%'
ORDER BY e.name;
